<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="layout" content="main"/>
    <title>Project Manager</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-md-4"></div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h1>Welcome to Project Manager</h1>
            <p>This is a simple project management web application. Written using the Grails framework.</p>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2> Features </h2>
                <p>Some of the main features are:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Multiple projects support</li>
                    <li>Multiple tasks support</li>
                    <li>Role based access control</li>
                </ul>
                <p/>
                <h2> Rules:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Any project can have many tasks.</li>
                    <li>Any task belongs to a single project, and can have many comments.</li>
                    <li>Any comment belongs to a single task.</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>
</html>
